toolkit.startup.max_resumed_crashes should be set to -1 in about:config for firefox
to prevent the safe mode popup from coming up!

need to install netifaces for python

To disable firefox cache:
browser.cache.disk.enable- set to false
browser.cache.memory.enable- set to false

to disable favicon, in about:config set
browser.chrome.favicons to false

to reduce how quickly os reverts to swap memory:
sudo sysctl vm.swappiness=20


empty href ("") in link tag when rel=shortcut icon leads to double fetch
https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=489115
